students who were vaccinated before 1980 or vaccinated between ages 
12 and 14 months in both cases the agency said studies have shown 
diminished vaccine effectiveness 
the twodose schedule and intensive efforts to raise 
immunization levels should facilitate the goal of measles 
elimination in the united states the cdc said 
