politan rejected that justification 
no law regardless of intent should have a chilling effect 
upon marriage the judge wrote in his opinion the court should 
encourage legitimate marriage not discourage it 
such broad brush regulations suggest mechanical 
computerlike answers to human problems of constitutional 
dimensions 
mrs hughes said more than 10 couples with similar problems 
across new jersey had contacted her about the case 
its going to make a lot of people out there happy she said 
