the justice minister ordered an investigation friday 
of allegations that movie director claude autantlara incited racial 
hatred with antisemitic comments 
the announcement came hours after the autantlara who also is a 
politician of the extreme right was forced to resign as vice 
president of the academy of fine arts 
pierre arpaillange the minister ordered the state prosecutor to 
investigate remarks attributed to autantlara in fridays edition of 
the monthly magazine globe 
his statement said the investigation could lead to charges of 
racial injury racial defamation and inciting racial hatred 
autantlara 88 stirred condemnation thursday when the magazine 
quoted him as saying french politician simone veil who survived a 
german concentration camp had been missed by the nazis 
in the interview was quoted as accusing ms veil 62 of 
exploiting her experience for political gain 
she plays the violins with that but she came back eh he 
was quoted as saying and shes doing very well so when they talk 
to me of genocide i say that in any case they missed old lady 
veil 
he was asked to give up the vice presidency of the academy of 
fine arts by the groups permanent secretary marcel landowski 
landowski declared himself profoundly shocked by the 
statements and joined fellow members in demanding autantlaras 
resignation from an assembly of artists in love with moderation 
and humanism 
last week autantlara stepped down as a member of the european 
parliament for the extreme rightwing national front without saying 
why 
national front leader jeanmarie le pen said the remarks about 
veil were shocking and completely open to criticism but 
also said the magazine was guilty of deliberatelyk making a scandal 
the ministry statement indicated the prosecutor also would 
determine whether to take action against the globe 
while not denying the remarks autantlara said earlier friday he 
reserved the right to sue the globe he said his telephone 
conversation with a globe reporter did not constitute an official 
interview 
autantlara directed such classics as the game of love the 
red inn and seven sins 
mrs veil a political centrist who served as president of the 
european parliament in 197981 and was reelected as a deputy in 
june has declined comment 
