and america providing cover 
the same thing is happening in lebanon where the leading role 
is being played by syria and israel but the american cover is much 
clearer and more candid than it was in the war with iraq 
in iraq the aim was to partition the country and in lebanon 
they have the same goal 
ramadan was interviewed thursday in belgrade at the summit 
conference of nonaligned nations a copy was telexed to the 
associated press in bahrain 
lebanon has been torn by 14 years of civil war 
