headway in ending the war since syria refused to agree to a 
timetable for withdrawing its troops 
let them try we are confident that hafez assad will not leave 
lebanon as a result of a resolution he merely wants to play for 
time 
the foreign ministers of saudi arabia morocco and algeria are to 
meet in jiddah saudi arabia next wednesday they will appraise the 
