attendants says easterns management is dismantling the airline and 
a change in ownership is needed 
eastern is trying to rebuild without its unions more than 650 of 
3600 alpa pilots at eastern have crossed picket lines since the 
strike began joining some 1000 newly hired pilots eastern 
recently announced it had stopped hiring new pilots 
